@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ofugma(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.exp(wp.abs(v0 + 0.45)) - wp.cos((v2 + 0.24 + v2 + 0.32)))
    v2 = (wp.cos((tmp + 0.98 + tmp + 0.00)) + 0.04)
    v0 = wp.exp((wp.cos(v1 + 0.19) - tmp))
    v1 = 0.21
    v1 = wp.sin(tmp)
    v0 = ((wp.sin(tmp + 0.30) * v1) * (v0 + v0))
    v1 = (wp.abs((v2 + 0.97 + tmp + 0.60)) * (0.78 + (tmp + 0.93 - v1 + 0.96)))
    data[tid] = v0
